item.title: Need help with this gay Run Server Error
item.dc:creator: @Stanyer Stanyer
item.description:
@Stanyer wrote:

  1. It’s not the RunServer.bat
  2. It’s definately that the server isn’t happy with your pc.
  3. If it’s just the text that’s bothering you, search for “[KERNEL]: machine is too slow to run this server!” in server.java and delete the misc.printIn line.
